	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "He agitated for the restoration of the powers of the tribunate (Sall. Hist. 3.48 M), and, perhaps in this year, accused C. Rabirius of sacrilege (Cic. Rab. Perd. 7; cf. Val. Max. 9.12.7)." .
